# dev-cache/ holds multi-GB frozen-world assets that nginx caches
# from upstream sources (HuggingFace, pytorch.org, ollama.com) plus
# the ollama model store (registry exception).
#
# Nothing in here should ever reach git. Rule: ignore everything
# except this file, the README, and the .gitkeep placeholders that
# let the bind-mount subdirs exist before first run.

*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!hf-cache/
!nginx-cache/
!ollama-data/
hf-cache/*
nginx-cache/*
ollama-data/*
!hf-cache/.gitkeep
!nginx-cache/.gitkeep
!ollama-data/.gitkeep
